---
---
<section class="booking section" id="reservar">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="booking-wrapper">
      <div class="booking-info">
        <p class="booking-label">Reservaciones</p>
        <h2>Reserve su Estadia</h2>
        <div class="gold-divider" style="justify-content:flex-start;"><span>&#9788;</span></div>
        <p>Complete el formulario y nuestro equipo de reservaciones le confirmara la disponibilidad en un maximo de 2 horas.</p>
        <div class="booking-guarantee">
          <span class="guarantee-icon">&#9733;</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Mejor precio garantizado</strong>
            <p>Reservando directamente obtendra el mejor precio disponible y beneficios exclusivos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="booking-contact">
          <p><strong>Reservas directas:</strong></p>
          <p><a href="tel:+5184234567">+51 84 234 567</a></p>
          <p><a href="mailto:reservas@casainti.pe">reservas@casainti.pe</a></p>
          <p class="whatsapp"><a href="#">WhatsApp: +51 984 567 890</a></p>
        </div>
        <p class="booking-policy">Cancelacion gratuita hasta 72 horas antes del check-in. Se requiere tarjeta de credito para garantizar la reserva.</p>
      </div>
      <form class="booking-form" action="#" method="POST">
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="checkin">Check-in</label>
            <input type="date" id="checkin" name="checkin" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="checkout">Check-out</label>
            <input type="date" id="checkout" name="checkout" required />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="guests">Huespedes</label>
            <select id="guests" name="guests">
              <option value="1">1 huesped</option>
              <option value="2" selected>2 huespedes</option>
              <option value="3">3 huespedes</option>
              <option value="4">4 huespedes</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="room">Tipo de Habitacion</label>
            <select id="room" name="room">
              <option value="inti">Habitacion Inti - $180</option>
              <option value="quilla">Suite Quilla - $280</option>
              <option value="imperial">Suite Imperial - $380</option>
              <option value="pachacamac">Suite Pachacamac - $520</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">Nombre completo</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Su nombre completo" required />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Correo electronico</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="su@email.com" required />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="requests">Solicitudes especiales</label>
          <textarea id="requests" name="requests" rows="3" placeholder="Celebraciones, preferencias alimentarias, hora de llegada..."></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold booking-submit">Solicitar Reserva</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .booking {
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .booking-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .booking-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .booking-info h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .booking-info > p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .booking-guarantee {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: rgba(184,134,11,0.08);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .guarantee-icon {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .booking-guarantee strong {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .booking-guarantee p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .booking-contact {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .booking-contact p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .booking-contact a {
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .booking-policy {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-style: italic;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(184,134,11,0.15);
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  .booking-form {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(184,134,11,0.15);
  }

  .form-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .form-group {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .booking-submit {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .booking-wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .booking-form { padding: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
